CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: City Office REIT Inc is a real estate investment trust. It is focused on acquiring, owning, and operating office properties located in metropolitan areas in the Southern and Western United States. The company owns office buildings in the metropolitan areas of Dallas, Denver, Orlando, Phoenix, Portland, Raleigh, San Diego, Seattle, and Tampa.
